        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", of general habits, “doings” of separate acts.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "I will cause you to dwell.—The English suggests the thoughts of something new, but what Jeremiah promises is simply the continuance of the blessings they had hitherto enjoyed. I will let you dwell.",
        "children": [
